<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Add photo sizes and prices</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<header>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-light">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">Меню</a>
        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarSupportedContent" aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>

        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-light">
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav">
                    <li class="nav-item active">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/users">Заказы <span class="sr-only"></span></a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/photos">Фотографии</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/sizes">Размеры фотографий</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/contacts">Пользователи</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </nav>
</header>
<body>
<h3>Список записанных размеров и их цены</h3>
    <table class="table">
        <tr>
            <th scope="col">Размер</th>
            <th scope="col">Цена</th>
        </tr>
        {{#prices}}
            <tr>
                <td scope="row">{{photo_size}}</td>
                <td scope="row">{{price}}</td>
            </tr>
        {{/prices}}
    </table>
    <h3>Добавить новый размер и назначить ему цену</h3>
    <form action="/sizes/add" method="post">
        <div><label>Размер фотографии:<input type="text" name="size"/> </label></div>
        <div><label>Цена за одну еденицу этой фотографии:<input type="text" name="price"/> </label></div>
        <div><input type="submit" value="Добавить"/></div>
    </form>
</body>
</html>